high_descs: Turn to the left, and then right to go to the sink.
Open the bottom left cabinet below the sink. Pick up the cloth from inside and shut the door.
Hold the cloth and look up at the sink.
Place the cloth in the sink and turn on the water. Turn off the water and pick up the cloth.
Carry the cloth and take a step to the left, look up to the mirror.
Place the cloth on the back of the toilet.
anns.task_desc: Rinse a cloth and place it on the toilet tank.

high_descs: Turn to the right, turn to the left and head to the left part of the sink
Open the cabinet door, remove the dirty cloth from inside and close the door.
Move slightly to the right and face the middle of the sink
Place the cloth on the left side of the sink, turn on the water to fill the sink and remove the cloth when it is clean.
Turn right three times and head to the toilet at the end of the sink
Place the cloth on top of the toilet's water tank.
anns.task_desc: Place a cleaned cloth on top of the toilet's water tank

high_descs: Walk ahead to the left basin of the sink.
Take the rag out of the cabinet on the bottom left.
Wash the towel in the sink.
Place the rag on top of the toilet tank.
anns.task_desc: Place a clean rag on a toilet tank.
